<strong>Mithril Two Handed Sword</strong>
<font size=-1>(<a href="/prices/item/mithril_two_handed_sword.shtml">View Going Price</a>)</font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">2H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 10.75<BR>
Damage 21 - Delay 40<BR>
Weight: 8.5 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/paladin/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/warrior/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">WAR</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/haste.shtml?spellID=683">Haste</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (Lore) <BR>
</font>
Dropped in Lower Guk by the Froglok King.<BR>
<BR>
Avg. Price Overall: 5480pp (114 quotes)<BR>
Last 30 Days: 2375pp (2 quotes)<BR>

