<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white> Easy to break this room with 4 people you dont need a monk or a sk or Feign death.<BR>
Used 4 players 2 necros with pets a Magician and a cleric, Broke room with pet assault. <BR>
Another way and its been done with 4 players. Attack the guards around the king and he wont get pulled have done this on 2 occasions.<BR>
If king is pulled you get 2 boks and the king root the boks or mez them if you have a enchanter and work the king over.<BR>
Then take the boks down one by one if need be seperate them so you dont get pounded.<BR>
Tiberious<BR>
